            AddTranslation("[creature] will move to and destroy any free, 1 health, non-terrain creatures played, and becomes stronger for each one consumed.", "[creature]将移而灭凡无主、1命、非地形之陈物；每噬一物，则更强。");
            AddTranslation("Rock Eater", "食石");
