            AddTranslation("Trampler", "践踏");
            AddTranslation("At the end of the owner's turn, [creature] will move in the direction inscribed on the sigil. Cards in the way will be killed, and grant +1 attack power to the sigil bearer.", "至主合末，[creature]循印所书之向而行。所当之牌皆亡，且令持印者得+1威。");
