            AddTranslation("Transmogrification", "易形");
            AddTranslation("When [creature] strikes a creature, that creature will be changed into another form.", "[creature]击物，则彼物易为他形。");
            AddTranslation("Trapjaw", "阱颚");
            AddTranslation("[creature] will attack to the left and the right of the opposing space if those slots are obstructed. If those slots are not obstructed, the strikes will be transferred to the directly opposing space.", "若[creature]对位之左右有阻，则击其左右；若无阻，则转击正对之位。");
